254
00:25:42,320 --> 00:25:45,471
Which Stanley?
The only Stanley in the world.

255
00:26:02,920 --> 00:26:05,309
Is there anything I can do for you, sir?

256
00:27:03,000 --> 00:27:08,120
Front boy! Stanley, take over
