I have to live it with you.

276
00:31:19,120 --> 00:31:20,712
- Shut it!
- Shut what?

277
00:31:20,880 --> 00:31:23,110
- Your big mouth.
- My big mouth?

278
00:31:23,280 --> 00:31:26,955
If you measured it,
you'd find my mouth is just a pinhole

279
