compared to the hollow tunnel
you've got.

280
00:31:29,760 --> 00:31:32,513
- You asked for it.
- Don't hit my husband.

281
00:31:32,680 --> 00:31:36,992
Young dog. Where do you come off,
butting in on our business?

282
00:31:37,160 --> 00:31:39,833
Don't you dare! How dare you?

283
00:31:40,000 --> 00:31:42,878
Busybody, nosy.
Mind your own business.

284
00:31:43,040 --> 00:31:46,476
Come on, honey.
Don't pay any attention to him.

285
00:31:46,640 --> 00:31:48,835
He don't know what he's talking about.

286
00:31:49,000 --> 00:31:50,911
My darling!

287
00:32:05,920 --> 00:32:10,596
I'm telling you, either you see to it that
your men are dressed neatly and clean

288
00:32:10,760 --> 00:32:12,830
or there's going to be trouble.

289
00:32:13,000 --> 00:32:16,390
We're not running a gymnasium.
This is a very high-class hotel.

290
00:32:16,560 --> 00:32:18,551
- Do you understand?
- Yes, sir.

291
00:32:18,720 --> 00:32:22,190
- I'll say it again. Neat, clean, nice.
- Yes, sir.

292
00:32:22,360 --> 00:32:27,718
Good taste, good clothes, refinement,
distinction. That is very, very important.

293
00:32:27,880 --> 00:32:30,348
Put this in my cabana.

294
00:32:31,160 --> 00:32:32,639
Bell captain.

295
00:32:32,800 --> 00:32:36,156
No, sir, I'm sorry,
you'll have to call room service.

296
00:32:36,320 --> 00:32:38,515
Company, halt!

297
00:32:38,680 --> 00:32:41,035
- Left face!
- Left face!

298
00:32:41,200 --> 00:32:44,829
