What do you want? A green light?

301
00:34:15,320 --> 00:34:17,197
Sit down and eat your food.

302
00:34:18,640 --> 00:34:20,392
And shut up!

303
00:34:21,400 --> 00:34:24,790
As I was saying,
when someone pushes you around

